HEADWORD: Hawhaw
<hw>Haw*haw"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Of imitative origin.]</ety>
<def>To laugh boisterously.</def> <mark>[Colloq. U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We <qex>haw-haw'd</qex>, I tell you, for more than half an
hour.</q> <rj><qau>Major Jack Downing.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

